public static sealed interface LogResponse.Status permits LogResponse.Status.ErrorStatus, LogResponse.Status.StandardStatus, LogResponse.Status.AggregateStatus, LogResponse.Status.MetricStatus
Log component status check. Note that trees or aggregates can be created with LogResponse.Status.AggregateStatus.
